Modifications summary:

  - Path resolution: directory layout under ~/.agent/ flattens upstream's
    .agent/ wrapper. Files preserve their __file__-relative path resolution
    logic; no code changes were required for this.
  - tools/render_lessons.py: extended _bullet_for() to render optional
    'why' and 'how_to_apply' fields when present in lesson rows. Backward
    compatible — when absent, output matches upstream.

